WEBVTT

00:01.310 --> 00:04.530
<i>Wealth, fame, power...</i>

00:05.490 --> 00:08.130
<i>Gold Roger, the king of the pirates,</i>

00:08.130 --> 00:10.900
<i>obtained everything
the world had to offer.</i>

00:10.900 --> 00:17.370
<i>His final words lured all sorts
of adventurers to the sea.</i>

00:17.370 --> 00:23.310
My treasure? 
It's yours, if you can find it.

00:23.310 --> 00:26.330
Everything is right where I left it!

00:26.330 --> 00:31.340
<i>Now pirates head for the Grand Line 
in pursuit of their dreams!</i>

00:31.930 --> 00:34.020
<i>The world has entered...</i>
